casebody.data:
Tuesday, September 9, 1997

MOTION DOCKET

96-1965. Disciplinary Counsel v. Holzer.

This matter is pending before the court upon the filing of an application of the city of Englewood and Eric A. Smith to intervene. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and is, hereby, denied.

Moyer, C.J., and Lundberg Stratton, J., dissent and would allow twenty days to respond.
